description: Log: Table containing logs from Ericsson radio access network equipment, including timestamps, location, cell IDs, log types, and severity.  Columns: dateTime (log timestamp), Area_Name (geographic area), CellId (unique cell identifier), Id2 (duplicate of CellId?), Id3 (unknown identifier), Id4 (log type), vsDataType (data type), vsDataFormatVersion (version), Log.severityFilter (severity filter), Log.logId (log identifier, potentially redundant with Id4), Log.reportProgress (progress indicator).
